      "difficulty": "medium",
      "constraints": "3 ≤ [[N]] ≤ 10 000\n1 ≤ height of a pile of dirt ≤ 1 000 000\nIt is guaranteed that there is at least one valid leap in the training ground, i.e. there is at least one combination of 3 piles where the middle pile is strictly higher than the other two.",
