      "stubGenerator": "read N:int\nloopline N height:int\nwrite MAXIMAL DIFFICULTY",
      "inputDescription": "<<Line 1:>> An integer [[N]] for the length of the training ground.\n<<Line 2:>> [[N]] space separated integers representing the ordered heights of each pile of dirt in the training ground.",
